<template>
	<div>
		<v-form v-model="valid">
    <v-container>
      <v-row>
        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="firstname"
            :rules="nameRules"
            :counter="10"
            label="First name"
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="lastname"
            :rules="nameRules"
            :counter="10"
            label="Last name"
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="email"
            :rules="emailRules"
            label="E-mail"
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </v-form>
</template>
<script>
export default {
	name: "edit_merchandise",
}
</script>
